-- David Beckham to Join Paris Saint-Germain on Five-Month Contract
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-01-31T16:47:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-31/david-beckham-to-join-paris-saint-germain-on-five-month-contract.html
English midfielder David Beckham
signed a five-month contract with Paris Saint-Germain, which has
spent more on players than any other European soccer club since
2011.  Beckham, 37, was introduced to the media and fans in Paris
today after passing a medical exam. PSG is tied with Lyon at the
top of Ligue 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  